{"tha-ap234:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap234:0.2":"Udakasanavagga ","tha-ap234:0.3":"2 Bhajanapalakattheraapadana ","tha-ap234:1.1":"“Nagare bandhumatiya, ","tha-ap234:1.2":"kumbhakaro aham tada; ","tha-ap234:1.3":"Bhajanam anupalesim, ","tha-ap234:1.4":"bhikkhusanghassa tavade. ","tha-ap234:2.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap234:2.2":"bhajanam anupalayim; ","tha-ap234:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap234:2.4":"bhajanassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap234:3.1":"Tepannase ito kappe, ","tha-ap234:3.2":"anantajalinamako; ","tha-ap234:3.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap234:3.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap234:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap234:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap234:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap234:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma bhajanapalako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap234:6.1":"Bhajanapalakattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}